Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.29,0:01:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.29,0:01:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a traveler seeking shelter from the rain.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.24,0:01:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be possible for me to spend the night here?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.06,0:01:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.02,0:01:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come inside and rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.79,0:01:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? A mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.83,0:01:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.16,0:01:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you feel unwell at all \Nor have noticed anything unusual,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.38,0:01:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be able to help.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.61,0:01:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything come to mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.57,0:01:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. We're actually pretty healthy.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.19,0:01:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the only thing that ails us
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.00,0:01:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is that, for all our toiling, \Nlife just never seems to get any easier.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.43,0:01:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.83,0:01:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned that you're a traveler... \NMaybe you could tell us about other lands.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.81,0:01:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us have left this village in a very long time.{lit: village}{x}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.30,0:02:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hospitality.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.37,0:02:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a pleasure listening to your strange tales.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.61,0:02:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had such average, unremarkable lives.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.14,0:02:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the best kind, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.96,0:02:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've got a point{,} there.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.98,0:02:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, take care.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.57,0:02:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. You too.
