Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder where the day went.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd better head home soon, or she'll start to worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The scent of flowers...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, this again.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just can't shake the feeling that I've forgotten something very important.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has this cave always been here?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or did someone dig it recently?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.25,0:04:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That flowery scent... It's coming from inside of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.33,0:04:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That means it must have an exit, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I can get home faster if I go through it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The scent is only getting stronger{overpowering} in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.95,0:04:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what could it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it that I've forgotten?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.49,0:04:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think... I'm starting to remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.12,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was... something that happened a long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Mother?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.35,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tea is ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.57,0:05:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, absolutely not!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.88,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Our sake's reputation is getting worse by the year.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to demand better pay,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.34,0:05:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,at least try making better sake first!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But with what you pay us now—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare talk back to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.95,0:05:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, that's nothing for you to worry about.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick that up for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.69,0:06:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that guy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru saw you do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.16,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you don't know how to apologize?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't apologize, then get out!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.32,0:06:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This one too...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.19,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Every last one of them has been drained?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.13,0:07:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Kaoru. Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't I know her from somewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.22,0:08:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... who was she, again?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.82,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.80,0:08:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's with this feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somehow...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this all feels really familiar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.87,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Iku!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me carry that for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.96,0:09:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something feels off...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.10,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can't quite put my finger on what it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.32,0:09:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's that feeling again.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's something I can't remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.23,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, I'm positive I've seen this cave before.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That flowery scent...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.09,0:09:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's coming from inside of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.20,0:09:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That must mean it has an exit.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should head back soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otherwise, she'll start to worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.25,0:10:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure I was about to remember something just now.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was it, though?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just can't remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.73,0:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And lately, everything feels really strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.72,0:10:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I've lived in this house my whole life...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.60,0:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it feels like just a distant memory at times.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.66,0:10:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, absolutely not!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.54,0:11:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For some reason, I can't shake the feeling that this has happened before.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.96,0:11:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.02,0:11:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's her!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.60,0:11:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But who was she, again?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.90,0:11:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? I'm certain this, too, has happened before...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.49,0:11:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a long, long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.49,0:11:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when was it, exactly?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just can't remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how much I try, I can't remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.01,0:12:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a traveler seeking shelter from the rain.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be possible for me to spend the night here?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.13,0:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? A mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.82,0:12:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you feel unwell at all \Nor have noticed anything unusual,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be able to help.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything come to mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.72,0:13:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... "Ginko," right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.68,0:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, something {\i1}has{\i0} been troubling me lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I can remember,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.81,0:13:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,there have been times when I see or \Nexperience something for the first time
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but feel like I've already seen it before...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.87,0:13:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or that it's happened to me already.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.58,0:13:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just my imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the same feeling right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.60,0:13:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I feel certain that I've let you stay at my home before, \Non a rainy night just like this one.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.15,0:13:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is my first time coming to these parts.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.89,0:13:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.54,0:13:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like it's anything serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.41,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I find it a bit disconcerting.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.25,0:13:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me wonder if it's just me, or if it happens to others too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.86,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Déjà vu, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.97,0:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel anxious when you smell flowers at night?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.67,0:14:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.96,0:14:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's usually when I feel like \NI've forgotten something.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.76,0:14:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.61,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have become trapped by a Kairou, \Nor "Looping Tunnel" mushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.57,0:14:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It's pitch-black and resembles a cavernous tube, \Nand it lures in insects and beasts by exuding a flowery scent.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.41,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And more pertinently, rumor has it \Nthat it warps its prey's time into a loop.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's truly the case,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.49,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,its prey may be forced to relive its life over and over.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Over and over...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.36,0:14:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can really confirm it for sure, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.90,0:14:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,if it actually is true,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.06,0:14:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's possible that you've {already }lived through your life many times over.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.09,0:15:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, it's also likely that you'll meet \Nthe Kairou again at some point in the future.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.32,0:15:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you unknowingly enter it yet again,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.66,0:15:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,time will repeat itself,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.52,0:15:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will re-experience your entire life.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.01,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There are indeed cases of déjà vu like yours,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's hardly possible to investigate them in full.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.53,0:15:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can know everything \Nabout someone else's whole life.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.67,0:15:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me... I've been living the same life over and over?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.23,0:15:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't say for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.17,0:15:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, I'd advise you to avoid \Nany dark places that give off a flowery scent.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.41,0:15:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}As far as I know, no one trapped by a Kairou has ever \Nmanaged to change the past into one of his own choosing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.40,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, now that you're this aware of your feelings of déjà vu,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.14,0:16:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you might not be able to \Nreturn to the past again.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.98,0:16:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,After going through the loop so many times, \Nyou might just end up becoming one with the Kairou.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.28,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever think of entering it again.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There {\i1}is{\i0} part of my past I'd like to change...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but more than that, \NI'd like to live out the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather see my daughter grow up...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.17,0:16:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and have children of her own, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.73,0:16:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see the part of my life I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.09,0:16:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Iku!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.99,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go gather some mountain vegetables.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.21,0:17:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder where the day went.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.28,0:17:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd better head home soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.92,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've gone through this cave, time after time...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}only to return to the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.18,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.96,0:18:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so late!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.27,0:18:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.71,0:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time seeing you like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.66,0:18:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel as though I've been \Nin a blissful nightmare all this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From this day on,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.13,0:18:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,every day will be a new day.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.74,0:19:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Iku!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Iku—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.78,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you to a doctor right away!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.29,0:19:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her body's getting colder...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.13,0:19:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do I do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might not make it back in time!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.52,0:19:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever think of entering it again.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.21,0:20:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Iku...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.12,0:20:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a flowery scent coming from inside of this cave.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can get home faster if we go through it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.89,0:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's going to be okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're definitely going to make it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.26,0:20:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And someday,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.44,0:20:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in the distant future,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.17,0:20:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll live with me again.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.70,0:20:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.41,0:20:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.77,0:21:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.24,0:21:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just now, it felt like I was \Njust about to remember something.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.76,0:21:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Iku, is something the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.68,0:21:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.55,0:21:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what could it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.29,0:21:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something so familiar,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.29,0:21:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yet strangely terrifying...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.56,0:21:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.53,0:21:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a traveler seeking shelter from the rain.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.57,0:21:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be possible for me to spend the night here?
